statements: SELECT * FROM property_inspections;
SELECT property_id, inspection_date, inspector_name FROM property_inspections WHERE inspection_result = 'Pass';
SELECT inspection_id, property_id, inspection_date, inspector_name FROM property_inspections WHERE inspector_name = 'John Doe';
SELECT * FROM property_inspections WHERE inspection_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT property_id, COUNT(inspection_id) AS total_inspections FROM property_inspections GROUP BY property_id;
SELECT * FROM property_inspections WHERE property_id = 10 ORDER BY inspection_date DESC;
SELECT inspector_name, inspection_result FROM property_inspections WHERE inspection_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT property_id, inspection_date, inspector_name FROM property_inspections WHERE inspector_name LIKE '%Smith%' ORDER BY property_id ASC, inspection_date DESC;
SELECT property_id, COUNT(inspection_id) AS total_inspections FROM property_inspections GROUP BY property_id HAVING total_inspections > 5 ORDER BY total_inspections DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT inspector_name FROM property_inspections WHERE inspection_result = 'Pass' ORDER BY inspector_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM property_management_companies;
SELECT company_name, company_address FROM property_management_companies;
SELECT company_id, company_name, company_address FROM property_management_companies WHERE company_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM property_inspections WHERE inspection_type = 'Fire Safety';
SELECT inspection_id, inspection_date, inspector_id FROM property_inspections ORDER BY inspection_date DESC;
SELECT company_name, company_address FROM property_management_companies;
SELECT * FROM property_management_companies WHERE company_id = 1;

SELECT company_name, inspection_date FROM property_management_companies JOIN property_inspections ON property_management_companies.company_id = property_inspections.property_id WHERE inspector_id = 123;

SELECT company_name, inspection_type FROM property_management_companies JOIN property_inspections ON property_management_companies.company_id = property_inspections.property_id WHERE inspection_type = 'Routine' ORDER BY company_name ASC, inspection_date DESC;

SELECT company_name, COUNT(inspection_id) AS total_inspections FROM property_management_companies JOIN property_inspections ON property_management_companies.company_id = property_inspections.property_id GROUP BY company_name HAVING total_inspections >= 5;

SELECT company_name, company_location FROM property_management_companies ORDER BY company_location DESC;

SELECT property_management_companies.company_name, commercial_buildings.building_name, property_inspections.inspection_date FROM property_management_companies JOIN commercial_buildings ON property_management_companies.company_id = commercial_buildings.company_id JOIN property_inspections ON commercial_buildings.building_id = property_inspections.building_id ORDER BY property_inspections.inspection_date ASC;

SELECT building_name, building_address, inspection_result FROM CommercialBuildings INNER JOIN Inspections ON CommercialBuildings.building_id = Inspections.building_id;

SELECT building_name, inspection_date, inspector_name FROM CommercialBuildings INNER JOIN InspectionSchedules ON CommercialBuildings.building_id = InspectionSchedules.building_id WHERE inspection_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY inspection_date ASC;

SELECT company_name, building_name, inspection_type FROM PropertyManagementCompanies INNER JOIN Inspections ON PropertyManagementCompanies.company_id = Inspections.building_id INNER JOIN InspectionSchedules ON Inspections.inspection_id = InspectionSchedules.schedule_id WHERE inspection_result = 'Pass';
